dcterms:description: A dataset containing more than 1.5 million grayscale image patches from three subsets: Liberty, Notre Dame, and Yosemite. It includes pairs of matching and non-matching patches used for training and evaluation of image patch matching algorithms.
dcterms:title: Multi-view Stereo Correspondence (MSC) dataset
